description: Stunning single-story country club estate offering breathtaking mountain views, situated on a unique 18,000 square foot lot, just a stone's throw away from Gilbert's exclusive private country club, Seville. This home has undergone a magnificent & recent renovation, showcasing an upgraded kitchen that radiates the elegance of a model home. The kitchen features brand new GE Cafe appliances, a central island, a cozy breakfast nook, & an exquisite backsplash that adds to its allure. The backyard resembles a luxurious resort, treating you to picturesque views, complete with a covered ramada, a built-in BBQ, and an outdoor bar beside a sparkling blue pool featuring a graceful waterfall. The expansive yard is an uncommon gem within this community. The open floor plan enhances the sense of spaciousness throughout the home. All of this splendor is nestled within the highly coveted Seville Country Club community, renowned for its two-story waterslides, 18-hole golf course, top-notch restaurants, fitness center, and an array of recreational amenities such as tennis and pickleball. Embrace the Seville lifestyle as you make this exceptional property your haven.

description: 3323 Hoctor Blvd in Omahas historic Deer Park neighborhood is a delightful single-family home. Constructed in 1914, it seamlessly marries timeless charm with modern comforts. The house boasts four spacious bedrooms, a well-maintained bathroom caters to household needs. The main floor features original hardwood flooring throughout the dining and living room, adding warmth and character. The kitchen, recently updated, is both functional and inviting, complete with a walk-in pantry for convenient storage. Whether youre preparing a family meal or hosting friends, this space caters to your culinary needs. Notable updates include a new roof, newer windows and new sliding as of 2022. Step outside to the fully fenced backyard, a private oasis for outdoor gathering or simply enjoying the fresh air. The parking pad behind the home isn't the only element of convenience. You'll also also this convenience location close to the zoo, downtown and more!

description: Welcome to 500 S Berendo #204, a move-in ready 1-bedroom condo nestled in the heart of Koreatown! Situated in one of the area's most coveted mid-rise buildings, this home boasts freshly painted interiors and ample natural light, creating a bright and welcoming atmosphere. The kitchen features sleek shaker-style cabinets and stainless steel appliances, including a refrigerator. A convenient in-unit laundry room with washer & dryer is just steps away. Living room features an inviting fireplace and access to your private balcony, and your spacious bedroom offers a tranquil escape, complete with a walk-in closet featuring custom organizers. Low monthly HOA dues cover water, trash, and secured building access with on-site management. Enjoy the convenience of two assigned tandem parking spaces and additional guest parking. Prime location just blocks from Wilshire Blvd and Vermont Ave, near all the shops and restaurants, and easy access to Metro Subway Vermont & Wilshire Stations. Don't miss out on this opportunity!

description: Welcome to Unit #221 at 125 N Allen Avenue! This charming unit is a large one bedroom ensuite condo with one walk-in closet and slider door wall closet. There is a guest bathroom and and large patio/ balcony for entertaining. Spacious living room has a fireplace. The dining room has sliding glass doors to the patio, as the living room does as well. The unit is located on the second floor, with elevator access. Laundry facilities are on the same floor as unit. HOA includes a pool, sauna, and workout room. The parking is gated and subterranean. Centrally located for easy access to Pasadena's shopping and dining, as well as PCC and Cal Tech. Close to freeway and Gold Line access.

description: Enter from the covered front porch into this spacious 4 bedroom home located next to a park! Beautiful hardwood floors throughout. Spacious family room overlooking the park.  Large living room off the kitchen/dinette with gas fireplace offering great space for family gatherings and beautiful views of mature trees.   Finished basement with full bath and egress with finished space currently used as office that can easily be converted to 4th bedroom.  Amazing outdoor space waiting for all of your summer gatherings with large patio and inground pool overlooking a beautiful park!  This lovely home is everything you could ever need! New roof 2022.

description: Welcome to Miami!!! Enjoy the contemporary, updated beautiful home in the desirable Miami Shores Neighborhood. This beautiful home features an updated open concept kitchen, with gray cabinets and quartz countertops, brand new wood vinyl flooring throughout and an updated bathroom. A nice den space that can be used as a bedroom or office space, with an attached one car garage. The property sits on a 9,150 square foot lot, with plenty of room to build a pool. Enjoy your private entrance through the rear of the home with parking for a boat or RV. This is it!! 15 minutes from South Beach, 12 minutes from Miami Airport and close to major highways, which gives easy access to South Florida's most popular attractions. WE ENCOURAGE ALL OFFERS

description: Welcome home to Carters Lane!!! This ranch is absolutely perfect for country living moments away from the amenities of Winchester and Stephens City, including it's close proximity to multiple farm markets such as the wildly popular West Oaks Farm Market (2 miles away).  Single level living at its best with over 3 acres of unrestricted land and ample storage, this home is rife with opportunity to create the ideal life you envision.  If you love to entertain or garden, the wide open outdoor spaces are perfect for you and your guests; the garden is already planted with delicious herbs including, but not limited to Oregano, Chocolate and Sweet Mint, Lemon Thyme and Garden Sage. Featuring additional amenities such as radiant ceiling heat for each room, a beautifully finished partial basement with a wood stove, full bathroom and it's own exterior entrance, a machine shed that can be a garage if needed, and much much more, Carters Ln offers it's new homeowners many cool features.  Upgrades to the home include a new Hot Water Heater (2020),  Finished Basement Flooring and Paint (2022),  Full Basement Bathroom (2022),  New Washing Machine (2022),  New Electrical Panel (2022)  and New Septic Lines (2016).

description: REMODELED SINGLE STORY POOL HOME located on a large private lot less than one mile from the beach. The home is built with quality and remodeled to perfection. Beautiful private and serene courtyard entry. Upon entry, you are greeted with an open floor plan. The chef's kitchen is complete with a 6 burner stainless steel range, hood, and quartz countertops. Down the hallway are 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The home was originally 4 bedrooms but was recently converted to a large art studio. Bedroom 4 can easily be converted back in place by adding a middle wall. Further down the hall, you will find a built-in desk area and a separate area with plenty of built cabinets for storage. The large master bedroom opens up to a peaceful veranda facing the backyard pool. The remodeled master bathroom is tranquil and serene. The large private backyard features a lap pool and plenty of room to dine alfresco. The professional landscaping and design enhance indoor & outdoor living. description: Enjoy the ease of one level living in this impeccably well maintained home. Designed and constructed by well-known builder Jim Henry, this quality all brick home offers a split bedroom floor plan, a kitchen that any cook will appreciate, and many options for you to enjoy the peaceful setting of this 1.8 acre property. New whole house Generac generator, new roof 2022, new 8x12 shed, hardwood and luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, lots of storage options, and more. Hike along the nearby neighborhood trails, work in the established garden, build a fire in the outdoor fireplace, or just sit and relax on your screened-in porch. This home has been well cared for and is ready for its next new owners.  Located within 15 minutes of UNC, Chapel Hill, or Pittsboro.

description: Gorgeous Ranch home offering 3 Beds, 3 Baths & an Attached 3 Car Garage ideally located backing up to Todd Creek Golf Course in the highly sought after Resort-style Gated community of Heritage Todd Creek. This Beautiful neighborhood is for active adults ages 55 & up offering many Amenities including a Restaurant, Clubhouse, Golf Course, Pools & more. Lovely curb appeal & a Welcoming Foyer invites you in to a Sunlit Open Floorplan boasting Amazing Golf Course views from your first steps inside. The  Living Room includes a Stone stacked Gas Fireplace for chilly evenings, Large Windows framing Picturesque vistas & engineered Wood Flooring flowing into the Kitchen & Dining area. Gourmet Kitchen is open to the Living Room & is a Chef's delight, boasting Quartz Countertops, SS Appliances, lots of Storage in the Bright White Cabinetry & a Walk-in Pantry. Large Island has Bar Seating, perfect for entertaining. The informal Dining area, also with Great Views, has a Glass Slider leading out to your Covered Composite Deck overlooking the Landscaped Yard, the Fenced Lawn area & out to the Golf Course. Stunning Primary Bedroom offers a Raised Tray Ceiling, Bay Windows overlooking the Backyard & beyond to the Golf Course. It has a Walk-in Closet & 4-Piece Bath with a Large Shower complete with Bench Seating & 2 Shower Heads. Main level includes a Guest Suite with a Full Bath, a 3rd Bedroom  & a 3/4 Bath. Conveniently located Laundry room with a Utility Sink and Cabinet is next to the Primary's Walk-in Closet. There's also a Mud Room with Garage access. Additional Amenities include central A/C, Ceiling Fans, raised Tray Ceilings & a Neutral Paint Palette. The Full Open 2,117 SqFt unfinished basement has tons of Space for Expansion and Storage. Enjoy an active Lifestyle in this community with a Fitness Center, Sport Courts, Indoor and Outdoor Swimming Pools as well as Educational opportunities, social gatherings and clubs. Quick easy access to 160th & E-470. See Virtual 3-D Tour.

description: ATTENTION INVESTORS and Buyers looking to build sweat equity! Come see the potential that this 5 bedroom, 3 story brick twin offers. Nestled on a one-way street, just 3 blocks off High Street, this property offers a convenient location with reduced traffic flow. The home has been occupied by its original owner for over 60 years and its now time for a new buyer to restore its charm and character. The main level with high ceilings offers a spacious floor plan that includes a vestibule entry, expanded living room, dining room, kitchen and shed leading to the fenced yard. There is plenty of room to expand the kitchen, add a powder room and laundry facilities and still have room left for a nice sized great room. The 2nd floor offers 3 bedrooms and 1 bath and the 3rd floor offers 2 bedrooms with one of the bedroom closets accessing the attic. The 3rd floor could potentially be converted into a primary bedroom with en suite bathroom. Some updates have been made, such as the gas heating system and related piping (2021), front porch floor and rails (2016), and replacement of the kitchen roof with some repairs to main roof and porch roof (2017). With the side yard along Mechanics Alley, theres potential to create off-street parking. This home needs work, offers lots of potential and is priced accordingly. It is being sold in as-is condition.

description: This may be the home for you! Built in 1946 and rehabbed in 2017, this amazing 1237 sq ft, 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath offers a classic lay out with a modern touch. Perfect for the buyer looking for a first time buyer with room to grow into with 2 first floor bedrooms, first floor full bathroom with a shower/tub and laundry nook on the first floor. The updated kitchen allows room for a small table, newer countertops and cabinets, stainless steel appliances that convey,  and open window views to watch kids or friends in the large fenced in backyard. The spacious living room greets you when you walk in with plenty of light and space and perfect for downtime for yourself or with your friends and family. The 2nd floor offers the 3rd bedroom coming in at almost 210 sq ft, with two ceiling fans, private 1/2 bath and a large closet. The 2nd floor also offers a privacy nook perfect for a home office. Into the fenced in backyard with dual entry points, you will find plenty of space for family gatherings and sitting by the firepit. The large detached powered garage comes with air conditioning, side entry, peg boarded walls, and work bench ready for those projects! Schedule your showing today!

description: Who's looking for SPACE in a newer home, located in a fantastic neighborhood, close to schools? Stop the Car!! THIS home provides 5 spacious bedrooms, an open and classic main floor layout that includes a formal dining room and home office! Check out the gorgeous stone fireplace in the hearth room that looks out the windows onto a cozy covered porch! The kitchen has tons of cabinets and counter space, with a large island that is the focal point of the whole area. The walk-in pantry is AMAZING with plenty of space for food and counter appliances. 4 spacious bedrooms upstairs and 3 full baths. Laundry room on the bedroom level. The master suite includes a sitting room for an additional office space as well as a magnificent master bath. The master bath is surround in beautiful tile, has a lovely walk in shower and separate tub, plus a double vanity and walk in closet.  The lower level includes a media room, 5th bedroom and full bath, that also walks out onto a lovely porch. The large lot is completely landscaped and looks absolutely breathtaking! description: Beautiful, move in ready home! Located in the wonderful Glenbrook tract, of the highly sought after Fair Oaks community. As you enter the home you are greeted by beautiful wood like laminate floors, and Vaulted ceilings.  Enjoy recess lighting throughout the home. The living room, and dining room are blended in one big space, and open up to the kitchen, giving you that great room feel. The kitchen has plenty of counter space, recess lights, and a newer stainless steel stove, and hood.  With no rear neighbors, the backyard is completely private, and quite spacious. All three of the bedrooms are located upstairs.  Every bedroom has plenty of natural light, is spacious, and has its own ceiling fan. The laundry room is conveniently located upstairs as well.  And, there is also a nice a little loft like area perfect to set up your home office. With the pandemic, working from home is the new norm, which makes this space a MUST HAVE! .  Last, but not least, the master bedroom is extremely generous in size, and a blank canvas, waiting for your personal style. The master bathroom features plenty of cabinet space for all of your linens. A Walk in closet, his and hers sinks, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Some additional upgrades, are a special air filter system, a water softener, and attic fans that provide more energy efficiency.  This home is just minutes off the 14 freeway, near major shopping, and only 30 min north of Hollywood. At, 575k THIS HOME IS A STEAL!!!

description: A wide paver walkway leads to the covered front portico of this lovely Addison Heights Colonial. Character abounds inside the charming front entryway complete with arched passageways into the dining room and kitchen. Natural light streams in from all sides through large windows, showing off the gleaming hardwood floors throughout the main and upper levels. A large living room boasts a full wall of custom, built in shelving and looks into the expanded and renovated eat-in kitchen. Generously proportioned formal dining room complete with corner cabinet and elegant chair-rail molding. Open concept, eat-in chefs kitchen boasts bar seating for three, abundant cabinetry, tons of granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, tile backsplash and large food pantry. Breakfast area feels like a sunroom with windows on three sides and features a bay window and a sliding glass door leading to the deck and overlooks the backyard. Convenient powder room on main level, an elegant stairway and banister lead to the upper level. Upper level includes three bedrooms, plumbing/ hook up for upstairs laundry and a large hall bathroom. Luxurious bathroom features dual vanity, oversized shower with glass enclosure and ceramic tile surround, deep soaking tub and plenty of storage. Large owners bedroom is big enough for a king-sized bed and a sitting area and boasts an envious walk-in closet as well as a second closet. Light and bright lower level features a fourth bedroom with egress window, rec room, second full bathroom, laundry room and utility room with storage space and separate entrance to the fully fenced backyard. Fantastic, flat and landscaped backyard features abundant grass, beautiful Trex deck, six foot tall white vinyl privacy fence and a meandering paver pathway on the side yard. A paver driveway fits at least two cars off the street, the home has dual zones for air conditioning, boiler provides heat through radiators throughout the home and this home has many, many recent updates and upgrades throughout. Supreme location within the most convenient neighborhood throughout the entire D.M.V. Zero stoplights to Washington D.C., close to Metro, schools, shopping, dining, grocery stores including Whole Foods. Easy access to The Pentagon, Amazons new National Landing HQ2 Headquarters, Virginia Tech Innovation Campus and so, so much more!

description: Your new home awaits, just in time for the Holidays!  This Beautiful 5 Bedroom 2.5 Bath home on a spacious lot in the charming Westlake Neighborhood with NO HOA is move in ready with numerous updates, you must see for yourself.  Your inner chef/cook will appreciate the remodeled Kitchen featuring chic white cabinetry, ample slab granite counters, in-cabinet lighting with glass doors, stainless appliances, pantry closet, breakfast nook plus it's open to the separate formal dining room.  The traditional layout includes a spacious Living Room, Kitchen and two dining areas plus half bath with newer wood laminate flooring on the main level, 4 Bedrooms upstairs including the Primary Bedroom with en-suite bath and updated guest bath.  The Basement is partially finished with drywall and Bedroom finished, rough-in bath, Laundry area and room for your future ideas...  Other notable features include updated/remodeled Baths throughout, roof, newer A/C, front and rear sprinkler system, hot water heater, cat 6 cable, lighting, brick and concrete patios and storage shed.  The neighborhood boasts numerous parks and trails, walking distance to Paul Derda Recreation Center, Broomfield Commons Open Space (incredible fireworks show from roof plus great planned events), public transportation, schools and close to The Bay Aquatic Park in the summer, shopping, restaurants and more...

description: A Colorado dream come true beautifully appointed villa in coveted Backcountry. Behind the gates you will find this home perfectly placed on an incredible cul-de-sac .20 acre lot backing to open space that offers sweeping mountain and city views. Imagine grilling on the covered deck w/gas line as you sip your favorite beverage & watch the sunset over the rocky mountains. Your beautifully landscaped yard, popping with color, mirrors the mountains as the sky glow changes from pink to orange. You have arrived! This stunning home with pristine Hickory wood floors comes complete with top-of-the-line details & finishes. Open chef's kitchen with warm white cabinetry features a 5 burner gas cooktop, custom vent hood, double ovens & large island with exquisite granite countertop. Sun filled morning room with door to deck is the perfect place to sip coffee as you watch the light reflect on the mountains. The kitchen opens to the great room with vaulted ceilings and corner gas fireplace. Lovely dining room offers additional space for gatherings with family & friends. Retreat to the luxurious primary bedroom suite which offers direct access to the covered deck & features a spa-like 5 piece bath, generous walk-in closet & main floor laundry. Your guests may never leave once they've settled into their private main floor suite. Descend the open sweeping staircase to enjoy the professionally finished walk-out lower level. With plenty of space for gaming, movie watching & entertaining this custom designed space with eye pleasing "beamed" ceilings and fabulous wet bar is loaded with light and includes an office space, 2 additional bedrooms & a bath with walk-in shower. Step outside to the covered patio and stunning backyard with mature landscape. Don't miss the attached three car garage with coated floor and loads of cabinets to store tools and toys out of site. HOA dues include front yard landscaping and snow removal to your door! This meticulously maintained home is a PERFECT 10.

description: Welcome to 15 S Brandywine, a classic twin in the heart of Modena Boro! Boasting a spacious front porch and a fenced-in front yard, this property invites you to experience the perfect balance of indoor and outdoor living. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the fresh ambiance created by new carpeting and a pristine white paint palette that graces every corner of the home. The main level unfolds graciously, beginning with a generously sized living room that seamlessly flows into the formal dining room. This open layout is ideal for entertaining friends and family or simply enjoying quiet evenings at home. The kitchen, located at the rear of the home, is completed with white shaker cabinets, newer linoleum flooring , and a convenient breakfast bar with seating for two, providing a cozy spot for casual meals or catching up over a cup of coffee. Just off the kitchen, a bonus room awaits, offering a view of the rear yard through its large window. This versatile space is perfect for a home office, a cozy reading nook, or a creative studio  the possibilities are endless. Ascending the stairs, you'll find a thoughtfully designed full bathroom that caters to your convenience, complete with a new vanity. The upper level hosts a spacious primary bedroom adorned with an abundance of natural light that highlights the serene atmosphere. Two additional bedrooms complete the floor, providing ample space for family members, guests, or hobbies. A practical unfinished basement presents the ideal solution for all your storage needs, keeping your living spaces clutter-free. A small landing with steps leading to the backyard adds a touch of functionality and access to the outdoors. 15 S Brandywine offers a unique opportunity to first time buyers looking for sweat equity & investors alike!  Don't miss the chance to make this property your new home sweet home! ALL OFFERS DUE BY SUNDAY AUGUST 13TH BY 7PM

description: Turnkey single story gem on a cul de sac with a pool sized backyard in the family friendly community of Shady Hollow. The owners have meticulously maintained and upgraded both the interior and exterior. The kitchen features granite countertops and newer stainless steel appliances.  Every inch of the back and side yards has new hardscape, landscape, irrigation as well as citrus trees and raised garden boxes. You'll love entertaining with the cozy firepit and built in gas BBQ fully equipped with a kegerator! The home is light and bright with dual paned windows and new LED lighting throughout and a new tankless water heater. Front bedroom has custom built-ins and custom closet doors. The Master also has custom closet doors and a custom master bath door. Encinitas Schools! This is truly a special home that will go fast! A must see!

description: Located in Eldersburg Estates on a landscaped .32 acre homesite is this amazing 2,872 square feet colonial with a Smart Home Alexa ready 2021 furnace, a NEST Thermostat, a southern style covered porch opening to bright interiors showing brilliant hardwoods, and refined crown moldings. Features include a formal living room, a dining room finished with crown molding and chair rail trim, a family room showing a Shiplap statement wall, followed by a well-equipped kitchen. Enjoy gourmet treats created in the cooks kitchen boasting 42 cherry cabinetry, granite counters, subway tile backsplash, newly installed stainless steel appliances with a professional exhaust, a peninsula breakfast bar, and a casual dining space with a French door walkout to the partially covered tiered deck with a pergola deck.  Owners suite presents a breezy ceiling fan, a walk-in closet, and private bath including a dressing area, a skylight, a double bowl vanity, and a separate bathing area.  Lower level showcases a rec room with built-ins and new carpeting, extra storage, a game room with walkout access and a granite wet bar with wine fridge, and a walkout to a fenced backyard.
